278
00:10:50,409 --> 00:10:52,244
DEVE TER CAÍDO
DO BOLSO DO MEU CASACO

279
00:10:52,328 --> 00:10:53,245
OU ALGO ASSIM.

280
00:10:53,329 --> 00:10:56,749
