(ISQUEIRO CLICA,
RANGE)

356
00:15:16,133 --> 00:15:17,384
(TEXTO CAI,
FOGO ESTALA)

357
00:15:18,385 --> 00:15:20,429
(ELI CAI NO PALCO)

358
00:15:20,512 --> 00:15:21,847
FIONA:
HUM...

359
00:15:23,265 --> 00:15:24,558
LUZES!

