376
00:16:38,924 --> 00:16:40,926
(PORTA FECHA)

377
00:16:44,596 --> 00:16:45,681
VOCÊ VAI FICAR BEM?

378
00:16:45,764 --> 00:16:47,766
(KC SUSPIRA PROFUNDAMENTE)

379
00:16:51,228 --> 00:16:53,188
