ESTUDANTIL

394
00:17:25,179 --> 00:17:27,931
CORRER TANTOS RISCOS
COM ELEMENTOS EXPERIMENTAIS.

395
00:17:28,015 --> 00:17:29,433
MUITO META!

396
00:17:29,516 --> 00:17:31,143
É, E TEVE ALGUMAS
RISADAS.

397
00:17:31,226 --> 00:17:32,311
É-É, É.

398
00:17:32,394 --> 00:17:33,979
UM HUMOR NEGRO,
COM CERTEZA.

399
00:17:34,063 --> 00:17:34,980
